PEANUT BUTTER COCOA NO-BAKE COOKIES

2 CUPS SUGAR
1 STICK BUTTER
3 TBLS HERSHEYS COCOA
1/2 CUT WHOLE MILK
PINCH OF SALT

Bring to boil and boil for 1 minute stirring constantly.
Remove from heat

Stir in 1/2 cup peanut butter, 2 tsp vanilla extract, 3 cups quick cooking quaker oats

drop tablespoonfulls onto wax paper.
cool completely in cool place.